{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0004","text":"但怎可找到伴侶讚賞","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["孤獨","渴望","認同"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["伴侶","讚賞","孤獨"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,9,9,9,4,2,5,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","zam2","ho2","zaau2","dou3","bun6","leoi5","zaan3","soeng2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"怎","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"找到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"伴侶","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"讚賞","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"提出反問，點出即使有成就，但缺乏伴侶的讚賞，加深孤獨感。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0005","text":"我 共你一樣(其實同樣痛)","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["共鳴","痛苦","相同"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["一樣","痛","共鳴"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,5,3,2,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","gung6","nei5","jat1","joeng6","sat6","tung4","joeng6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"共","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一樣","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"其實","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"同樣","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"痛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"}],"syntax_notes":"直接表達與聽者（或某人）的相同之處，括號內補充說明這種相同是痛苦的，帶有自嘲和無奈。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0006","text":"天生天養(痛得大過天)","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["宿命","痛苦","成長"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["天生天養","痛","成長"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,5,3,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","sang1","tin1","joeng5","dak1","daai6","gwo3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天生","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"天養","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"(","pos":"PUNCT"},{"text":"痛得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"大過天","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":")","pos":"PUNCT"}],"syntax_notes":"「天生天養」帶有宿命論的意味，括號內再次強調痛苦的程度，暗示成長的代價。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0007","text":"我們同樣受過傷","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["共同經歷","創傷","理解"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["受過傷","共同","創傷"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,0,0,2,2,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","mun4","tung4","joeng6","sau6","gwo3","soeng1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我們","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"同樣","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"受過傷","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"直接點出「我們」都曾受過傷，為後續的「相通」鋪墊，情感上帶有共鳴。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0008","text":"難受要是要是能相通","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["理解","和解","放下"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["相通","理解","放下"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,2,4,2,0,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["naan4","sau6","jiu3","si6","jiu3","si6","nang4","tung1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"難受","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"要是","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"要是","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"相通","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"提出一個假設，如果能夠互相理解（相通），那麼難受的情緒就能被放下，語氣轉為積極。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0009","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0009","text":"仇恨也就放下能相擁","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["和解","擁抱","放下"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["相擁","放下","和解"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,2,4,2,0,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["sau4","han6","jaa5","zau6","fong3","haa6","nang4","jung2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"仇恨","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"就","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"放下","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"相擁","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"承接上一句，說明理解後可以放下仇恨，進而能夠相擁，情感更加積極。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0010","text":"縱使痛 亦覺得傷口是場夢","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["痛苦","釋懷","夢境"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["痛","傷口","夢"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,9,4,2,4,3,3,9,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zung3","si2","tung3","jik6","gok3","dak1","soeng1","hau2","si6","coeng4","mung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"縱使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"痛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"亦","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"覺得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"傷口","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"場","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"夢","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"即使感到痛苦，但因為能夠理解和釋懷，傷痛的感覺就像一場夢，語氣趨於平靜。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
