{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0014","text":"人 總有下場 一炮雙響 一對一雙","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["伴侶","成功","圓滿"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["雙響","一對","圓滿"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,5,2,0,3,4,3,9,3,4,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jan4","zung2","jau5","haa6","coeng4","jat1","paau3","soeng1","hoeng2","jat1","deoi3","jat1","soeng1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"人","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"總有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"下場","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"一炮","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"雙響","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一對","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"一雙","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描繪了人最終會找到伴侶，並且能取得成功（一炮雙響），達到圓滿的狀態。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0015","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0015","text":"什麼悲傷也像中獎","structure":{"line_index":15,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["幸運","轉變","喜悅"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["中獎","悲傷","轉變"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,3,3,3,5,2,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["sam6","mo1","bei1","soeng1","jaa5","zoeng6","zung1","zoeng2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"什麼","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"悲傷","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"像","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"中獎","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"將悲傷比喻為中獎，表示悲傷的感覺被喜悅所取代，語氣充滿幸運感。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0014","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0016","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
