{"id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0017","text":"便懂得怎去爲你設想","structure":{"line_index":17,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["體諒","關懷","設想"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["設想","體諒","關懷"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,9,3,9,4,5,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bin6","dung2","dak1","zam2","heoi3","nei5","cit3","soeng2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"便","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"懂得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"怎去","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"爲","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"設想","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"從被傷害的經驗中學習，懂得為對方設想，語氣轉為積極和體諒。"},"source":{"title":"天下有雙","artists":["Twins"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4838","prev_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0016","next_line_id":"lyr_VHdpbnM_NDgzOA_0018","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
